text: Monroe Township is a township in Middlesex County, New Jersey, United States. As of the 2020 census, 48,594 people lived there.DP-1 - Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics: 2010 for Monroe township, Middlesex County, New Jersey , United States Census Bureau.
